  "body": "The new QBFT transition for changing the validator selection mode does use the correct header validation rules if there is a non validator selection transition.\r\n\r\nE.g. Starting in contract validator mode and changing the block reward at block 5. From block onwards the incorrect block header validation rules are being used. This results in the chain stalling.\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"config\": {\r\n\"chainid\": 2017,\r\n\"homesteadBlock\": 0,\r\n\"eip150Block\": 0,\r\n\"eip155Block\": 0,\r\n\"eip158Block\": 0,\r\n\"byzantiumBlock\": 0,\r\n\"qbft\": {\r\n\t\"epochlength\": 30000,\r\n\t\"blockperiodseconds\": 5,\r\n\t\"requesttimeoutseconds\": 10,\r\n\t\"validatorcontractaddress\": \"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000008888\"\r\n},\r\n\"transitions\": {\r\n\t\"qbft\": [\r\n\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\"block\": 5,\r\n\t\t\t\"blockrewardwei\": 20\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t]\r\n}\r\n```",
